              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Al plates with thin 232Th and 238U layers deposited",
                " from two sides.",
                "The distance between the plates was fixed using",
                " inserts.",
                "Thin Al portable foils (ten in number) were inserted",
                " in the gap between plates before irradiation.",
                "Under irradiation, high energy fragments were formed as",
                " a result of fission: some of them were knocked in the",
                " portable foils."
              ]
            }
          ],
